http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Hyderabad/An-evening-with-the-mystic/article13975810.ece

ISHA Foundation, an NGO, will conduct a unique spiritual programme by Sadhguru Jaggi Vasudev titled ‘An Evening with the Mystic’, in Hyderabad, Tirupati and Visakhapatnam. In Hyderabad, it will be held at JRC Convention Hall in Filmnagar between 4 p.m. to 8 p.m. on January 2.The event will feature discourses, meditations, questions-and-answer sessions and an exposure to techniques developed by the Sadhguru.For more information and participation, mail to hyderabad@ishayoga.org or browse the website www.isha.sadhguru.org/yoga-classes /hyderabad .